---
/**
 * FAQSection.astro
 * Frequently asked questions - handles objections
 */
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Common Questions <span class="text-red-600">Answered</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Everything you need to know before you call.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Accordion -->
    <div class="space-y-4">

      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 list-none">
          <span>How quickly can you respond to an emergency?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>We typically respond within <strong>2 hours or less</strong> for emergency calls. During extreme weather, we prioritize no-heat emergencies and aim to have a technician at your door as fast as possible — often same-day. We're available 24/7/365 for true emergencies.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 list-none">
          <span>What does the $125 home visit include?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Your $125 diagnostic visit includes:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Complete system analysis by a licensed technician</li>
            <li>Written assessment report with findings</li>
            <li>Transparent repair pricing (no hidden fees)</li>
            <li>Expert recommendations and maintenance tips</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3"><strong>Best part:</strong> If you proceed with recommended repairs, the $125 fee is <strong>fully credited</strong> toward the work. You only pay if you decline repairs or choose another contractor.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 list-none">
          <span>Are your technicians licensed and insured?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Absolutely. Every Fix My Furnace technician is:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Michigan-licensed</strong> HVAC professionals</li>
            <li><strong>Fully insured</strong> with liability and workers' compensation coverage</li>
            <li><strong>Background-checked</strong> for your safety and peace of mind</li>
            <li><strong>Continuously trained</strong> on the latest heating technology and safety standards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 list-none">
          <span>What areas in Michigan do you serve?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>We proudly serve <strong>all of Michigan</strong>, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Detroit Metro Area</li>
            <li>Grand Rapids & West Michigan</li>
            <li>Ann Arbor & Washtenaw County</li>
            <li>Lansing & Central Michigan</li>
            <li>Flint, Kalamazoo, and beyond</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">From the Upper Peninsula to the Ohio border — if you're in Michigan, we've got you covered.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 list-none">
          <span>Do you offer financing or payment plans?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Yes! We understand that furnace repairs and replacements can be unexpected expenses. We offer flexible financing options and payment plans to make quality heating affordable. Ask your technician for details during your visit.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:border-red-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 list-none">
          <span>What if my furnace can't be fixed?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>If your furnace is beyond repair, we'll give you honest recommendations for replacement options. We'll walk you through:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Energy-efficient furnace models that fit your home and budget</li>
            <li>Available rebates and incentives</li>
            <li>Installation timeline and process</li>
            <li>Financing options to make it affordable</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We'll <strong>never</strong> pressure you into a replacement if a repair will do. Your trust matters more than a single sale.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
